{"tid":757610,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"搵工搵到好灰","createTime":"2018-07-27T04:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T04:23:47.000Z","uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1d05f45ce86020074b84276b49a7efc94e71afb7","tid":757610,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T04:02:27.000Z","msg":"17年個陣Ive grad 仲要係無撚用既科<br />\n然後走左去做local brand pt sales<br />\n因為時薪ok+commission好易追所以一做就做左年幾<br />\n後黎頂唔順store man同想搵ft跳左去另一間second end既brand做pt<br />\n同事關係好好 同埋知道ft福利好到仆街<br />\n返工車程15分鐘<br />\n8日例假 生日多一日 <br />\n14日大假<br />\n唔到數既話都會有16k 到左有兩皮<br />\nPath幾易升 <br />\n準時收工<br />\n缺點就係試用期幾難過同埋要同班客whatsapp（不過我接受到）<br />\n除左星期六日忙少少其他日子hea到乜咁<br />\n<br />\n好 講返正題<br />\n事關老母屌我讀咁多書走去做sales<br />\n於是我走去send cv文職同考政府工<br />\n但一直撞板又考唔到 而家真係好灰<br />\n我份人又好怕悶 同埋福利待遇真係比唔上而家做緊個間<br />\nSales又識到唔同人又趁後生先有優勢<br />\n個人想做sales行行企企多過文職坐office...<br />\n我應該同老母三六口面講清楚定繼續搵工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4cbc654ce0e7cb047cf863ea38d7f80951b22e","tid":757610,"uid":59570,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T04:17:25.000Z","msg":"你想做咩咪做咩<br />\n<br />\n而家你老母返工定你返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d282e687396e467145a4eb75746e2b97d29bb5f","tid":757610,"uid":166506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T04:19:22.000Z","msg":"忠於自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdee3233c232e2c717fcf2f979fee0b199041d69","tid":757610,"uid":163783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T04:23:47.000Z","msg":"ive in 政府工只能做最低階狗"}]}